\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Di ako. Si Faye umisip nyan. The funeral's the only way to get them all together in one place. Mas-madali din to kasi imposibleng magsinungaling yung suspect kung nandyan yung iba para kontrahin sila. \par
