\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql But it's ideal to go where the witnesses are gathered if I wanted to clean up loose ends. Speaking of, bakit ka nga ba nandito ulit? Lahat kasi ng nandito, witnesses. The rest are invited guests. We invited them para hindi mag-panic yung mga potential suspects.\par
