\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Epol, Apol. You can say them differently but they're the same thing. Loser.\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql *laughs* Hate to admit it but I'm getting used to your rudeness. And what do you call your failure?\

\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql It was a set up. An elaborate plan set to fuck me up. And I'm here to make the person responsible pay.\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql And who is this person who effed you up?\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Correction, people who fucked me up. So here's the deal. Have you heard of the Zalameda case?\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql The missing diamonds? Remotely.\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Yep. So this is the case that Miko and Karl Simon were working on. The case that lead to his death. I always admired Karl's work. He's that badass detective that stops at nothing to achieve his goal. Anyway, so the case lead to a dead end. That's why they closed the case and Miko was killed a week after, presumably related to the case.\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql How did he die?\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql *Gets mad and punches stuff* (Raised voice) SHUT! UP! And let me talk! *sighs* (Normal voice) I can't tell you, cause of death can't be revealed until the case is solved. \par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql I'm already working on the case with you. Dali, telme! \par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Slow and brutal death. That's why the coffin is covered.\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql ANGELO\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql So, you reopened the case?\par
\pard\plain \s3\f0\caps\fs24\sb240\fi0\ql MICHAEL\par
\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb120\fi0\li694\ri694\ql Yes. I reopened the investigation and guess what? Everything was redtaped! They wouldn't let me look at evidence nor reports and the worse part is I got laid off from the force. Someone influential didn't want the case reopened. I lost my freaking job! Those sons of bitches cost me my job! I was this close to a promotion! AHHH! MOTHERF*! TANG!\par
